data.text:
Education

University of Missouri-Kansas City School of Law, JD, 2015

University of Missouri-Columbia, BA, 2011

Nate is a partner in the firms Chicago office and has focused his career on insurance-related litigation, having begun his practice as an associate attorney with an insurance defense firm in Illinois. He has experience representing clients in a number of civil litigation specializations, including personal injury, construction liability, product liability, premises liability, toxic torts, accounting malpractice, and commercial transportation. As part of his practice, Nate is involved in all aspects of litigation from discovery through trial. In addition to his defense practice, Nate has experience representing and counseling insurance companies in litigation and disputes involving insurance coverage issues as well as handling complex commercial transactions.
